OL,3,CGreens will be kingmakers in Wales,
OL,4,Csay party leaders
OL,6,FWelsh Greens stand ready to be "the
OL,7,Fkingmakers" in the Senedd, according
OL,8,Fto their leader here and the head of
OL,9,Fthe party in Wales and England.
OL,11,FAnthony Slaughter and Zack Polanski
OL,12,Fsaid that meant it could be Green
OL,13,FSenedd Members holding the balance
OL,14,Fwhen it comes to forming a government.
OL,16,FThe Green Party launched its campaign
OL,17,Ffor the Welsh parliamentary election
OL,18,Ftoday with polls predicting an
OL,19,Funprecedentedly good set of results.
OL,26,@nD@`OUoD@KO]
