OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775139065
OL,3,CGreens will be kingmakers in Wales,
OL,4,Csay party leaders
OL,6,FThe latest YouGov poll for ITV Cymru
OL,7,FWales and Cardiff University puts the
OL,8,Fparty on a 12% share of the vote that
OL,9,Fcould translate into as many as 10
OL,10,Fseats in the new chamber. It would be
OL,11,Fa major breakthrough for the Greens
OL,12,Fwho have never had a Senedd member.
OL,14,FThere'll be a new, more proportional
OL,15,Felectoral system for the vote on 7 May
OL,16,Fwhich makes it highly unlikely that
OL,17,Fany one party could win a majority of
OL,18,Fseats.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
