FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775139065
OL,3,CGreens will be kingmakers in Wales,
OL,4,Csay party leaders
OL,6,FOur most recent poll suggests that
OL,7,FPlaid Cymru and Reform UK will be
OL,8,Fvying to become the biggest party, but
OL,9,Fwithout the necessary number of seats
OL,10,Fto form a government alone.
OL,12,FThat could put the Greens in a
OL,13,Fpowerful position, according to senior
OL,14,Fparty figures.
OL,16,FThe leader of the Green Party of
OL,17,FEngland and Wales, Zack Polanski, told
OL,18,Fmembers at their campaign launch that
OL,19,F"The Greens could be the kingmakers at
OL,20,Fthis election."
OL,26,@{D@AOU|D@OO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
