CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775139065
OL,3,CGreens will be kingmakers in Wales,
OL,4,Csay party leaders
OL,6,FHe added that, "That means we know
OL,7,Fthere will be a new government in
OL,8,FCardiff Bay, and what the colour of
OL,9,Fthat government look like and the mix
OL,10,Fis ultimately up to the voters.
OL,12,F"But we're being very clear. Every
OL,13,Fsingle Green that is elected to the
OL,14,FSenedd will be a Green in those
OL,15,Fnegotiations who is standing up for
OL,16,Frent controls to make sure we're
OL,17,Fbringing down water bills by working
OL,18,Ftowards public ownership of the water
OL,19,Fcompanies, and a fairer deal by
OL,20,Fabolishing council tax and replacing
OL,21,Fit with a land value tax."
OL,26,@nD@POU}D@ZO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
