OL,3,CGreens will be kingmakers in Wales,
OL,4,Csay party leaders
OL,6,FThe party is yet to publish its
OL,7,Fmanifesto, but those last three points
OL,8,Frepresent its main pledges as repeated
OL,9,Fby senior figures in recent weeks.
OL,11,FWelsh leader, Anthony Slaughter, told
OL,12,Fthe activists to campaign for every
OL,13,Fvote, adding that "it has never been
OL,14,Fmore important or more urgent that we
OL,15,Fget that group in. And as Zak has
OL,16,Falluded to, we will be the kingmakers.
OL,26,@uD@SOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
