PN,46806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775139065
OL,3,CGreens will be kingmakers in Wales,
OL,4,Csay party leaders
OL,6,F"We will be deciding and directing the
OL,7,Fdirection of the next Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment. And at a time of cost of
OL,9,Fliving crisis, nature degradation and
OL,10,Fclimate chaos, our voice, our policies
OL,11,Fhave never been more needed.
OL,13,F"We will stand up. We will make sure
OL,14,Feveryone has access to a safe, secure
OL,15,Fhome, affordable housing.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
