OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775139065
OL,3,CGreens will be kingmakers in Wales,
OL,4,Csay party leaders
OL,6,F"We will start with protecting tenants
OL,7,Frights, starting with an immediate
OL,8,Frent freeze, moving on to rent
OL,9,Fcontrols, building social housing, the
OL,10,Fscale and pace needed, replacing the
OL,11,Fbroken council tax system with land
OL,12,Fvalue tax, making sure that the
OL,13,Fwealthiest in this country pay their
OL,14,Ffair share.
OL,16,F"And we will clean up our rivers. Our
OL,17,Frivers are so full of sewage. We will
OL,18,Fbring Dwr Cymru back into public
OL,19,Fownership through that. It's not going
OL,20,Fto be easy, but it is doable. It needs
OL,21,Fto happen."
OL,26,@zD@Hs{}D@KO]
